data.description: This stunning 2022-built home, situated near the Red Hawk golf course and conveniently close to Highway 70, boasts four bedrooms and three full bathrooms. One bedroom features an en suite bathroom. Upon entering, the high ceiling in the foyer adds an elegant touch. The main living area follows an open concept with a dining area adjacent to the kitchen and living room, the latter featuring an electric fireplace. The gourmet kitchen offers an island with a breakfast bar, granite countertops, pantry, ample cabinet space, a gas cooktop stove, and a coffee nook. The master bedroom, part of a split plan, includes a spacious bathroom with a double vanity, garden tub, separate shower stall, and a large walk-in closet. As you step into the backyard, enjoy the breathtaking views of the Organ Mountains. The landscaped backyard requires minimal maintenance. Come check it out before its too late!
